en-US.summary: Get the latest and greatest from Overheard LA
examplePhrases: Alexa ask ya heard for a quote
Alexa tell ya heard to tell me some quotes
en-US.name: Ya Heard
en-US.description:
Ask for Ya Heard, and learn about what really matters, like an Angeleno's take on committment.

Ya Heard provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you think less of Los Angeles.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Ya Heard" or "Alexa, open Ya Heard" to get a quote".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
